<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1 class="display-5 text-center">Burger Annihilator</h1>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 mx-auto my-2">
      <p class="lead text-center">This is a simple hero unit, a simple jumbotron-style component for calling extra attention to featured content or information.</p></div>
